Package: lettercase
Title: String format utilities for consistent capitalization and word breaks
Version: 0.11
Authors@R: "Christopher Brown <chris.brown@decisionpatterns.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Utilities for formatting and manipulating character vectors for
    cases such as snake_case, Title Case, UPPERCASE, lowercase, etc.; lettercase
    provides a simple, consistent, intuitive and high performing interface for
    implemting standards for character, strings, text and names.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    magrittr (>= 1.0.1),
    stringr (>= 0.6.2)
Suggests:
    testthat
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Collate:
    'lettercase-package.R'
    'make_names.R'
    'make_str_replace.R'
    'patterns.R'
    'str_cap_words.R'
    'str_delete.R'
    'str_functions.R'
    'str_is.R'
    'str_lowercase.R'
    'str_sentence_case.R'
    'str_snake_case.R'
    'str_spine_case.R'
    'str_title_case.R'
    'str_transform.R'
    'str_ucfirst.R'
    'str_uppercase.R'
    'utils.R'
    'zzz.R'
